Games-Nurikabe-Solver

This aims to be an automated solver for Nurikabe. It will serve as a prototype,
and a way to play around with the elements of a Nurikabe Solver.

More about Nurikabe:

* http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nurikabe

* http://www.logicgamesonline.com/nurikabe/

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Games::Nurikabe::Solver

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Games-Nurikabe-Solver

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Games-Nurikabe-Solver

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Games-Nurikabe-Solver

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Games-Nurikabe-Solver


